    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate adequate agreement between CFD predictions and FDA experimental benchmark data across all five operating points. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
